Title: Learn to Solder (and Upgrade Your Badge!)
Book Description: Soldering is the process of using heat to fuse metal with metal.  We will teach you how to use this skill to create (or repair) your own electronics projects- and you will get a fancy Penguicon LED badge to prove it! Already have a fancy LED badge? Make it better! We will provide microcontroller programmers for those who wish to change their badge's microcontroller code.  Write programs in AVR C to fashion new blinky badge sequences- or create a simple badge-based game!

Title: Penguicon Robot Build
Book Description: Come help design and build a robot during the convention. Donations may be accepted depending on the robot design. No skill necessary to help but prior experience would be useful. Useful skills include familiarity with microcontrollers- structural design- costume design- programming- graphic design- and logic!
